        {
            "id": 6011495,
            "title": "川普很快會公布下任Fed主席人選 點名華許備受好評",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>美國總統川普週五 (6 日) 表示，關於下一任聯準會 (Fed) 主席的人選，決定將很快公布，並強調一位「好的聯準會主席」應該會降息。</p></section><p></p><div class=\"c1hvmcli\"><figure><div class=\"iirgi4a\"><img alt=\"cover image of news article\" class=\"cr8g41v\" data-nimg=\"fill\" decoding=\"async\" fetchpriority=\"high\" sizes=\"\n            (max-width: 1024px) 100% 406px,\n            (max-width: 768px) 100% 193px\n          \" src=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011495%2Fl%2Fcaa1365242fc2afda88dea5787ab4d3b.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\" srcset=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011495%2Fl%2Fcaa1365242fc2afda88dea5787ab4d3b.jpg&amp;w=16&amp;q=75 16w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011495%2Fl%2Fcaa1365242fc2afda88dea5787ab4d3b.jpg&amp;w=32&amp;q=75 32w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011495%2Fl%2Fcaa1365242fc2afda88dea5787ab4d3b.jpg&amp;w=48&amp;q=75 48w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011495%2Fl%2Fcaa1365242fc2afda88dea5787ab4d3b.jpg&amp;w=64&amp;q=75 64w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011495%2Fl%2Fcaa1365242fc2afda88dea5787ab4d3b.jpg&amp;w=96&amp;q=75 96w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011495%2Fl%2Fcaa1365242fc2afda88dea5787ab4d3b.jpg&amp;w=128&amp;q=75 128w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011495%2Fl%2Fcaa1365242fc2afda88dea5787ab4d3b.jpg&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 256w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011495%2Fl%2Fcaa1365242fc2afda88dea5787ab4d3b.jpg&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011495%2Fl%2Fcaa1365242fc2afda88dea5787ab4d3b.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011495%2Fl%2Fcaa1365242fc2afda88dea5787ab4d3b.jpg&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011495%2Fl%2Fcaa1365242fc2afda88dea5787ab4d3b.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011495%2Fl%2Fcaa1365242fc2afda88dea5787ab4d3b.jpg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011495%2Fl%2Fcaa1365242fc2afda88dea5787ab4d3b.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011495%2Fl%2Fcaa1365242fc2afda88dea5787ab4d3b.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011495%2Fl%2Fcaa1365242fc2afda88dea5787ab4d3b.jpg&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6011495%2Fl%2Fcaa1365242fc2afda88dea5787ab4d3b.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\"/></div><figcaption class=\"c1gcnfq1\">川普很快會公布下任Fed主席人選 點名華許備受好評 (圖：REUTERS/TPG)</figcaption></figure></div><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>鮑爾任期 2026 年 5 月結束，當被問到下屆人選何時出爐？川普在空軍一號上對記者表示：「這件事很快就會宣布。」</p></section><section>\n</section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>被問及是否考慮前聯準會理事華許 (Kevin Warsh) 時，川普說：「他備受好評。」</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>外界普遍認為華許是川普下一任聯準會主席的熱門人選之一。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>華許在 2006 年 2 月到 2011 年 4 月擔任聯準會理事，他是由美國前總統小布希 (George W. Bush) 任命。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>週五稍早前，川普也表示聯準會應該大幅降息一個百分點，並再次批評現任主席鮑爾 (Jerome Powell) 行動太過遲緩。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>川普第二次任期以來，他多次公開抨擊鮑爾未能按照他的期望降息。兩人上週首度面對面會談，川普當面告訴鮑爾，他未降息是個「錯誤」。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>《華爾街日報》4 月報導，美國總統川普長達數月私下討論撤換鮑爾，並在今年 2 月在佛州海湖莊園 (Mar-a-Lago) 與華許討論撤換鮑爾。華許則建議川普不要試圖撤換鮑爾，而是應該讓聯準會主席做完任期不去干預。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
